# Terraform local state and working files — never commit these
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
crash.log
crash.*.log

# terraform.tfvars can hold environment-specific values — keep the .example committed, not this
# (uncomment if your tfvars ever holds anything sensitive)
# terraform.tfvars

# Terraform's provider version lock file is the ONE thing you WANT committed —
# do not add .terraform.lock.hcl here.
